                <p class="solar-header-item">預估內部報酬率<span>{{LOAN_INTEREST_RATE}}％</span></p>
                <a onclick="return MemOnSaleLoanCaseChk(this,'{{CASE_NO}}',{{USR_PANELS_NUM}} )" href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn--common btn--common-1 btn-sell">我想出售</a>
